profile_reset:
REVOKE ALL
    ON DATABASE {dbname}
    FROM {username};
REVOKE ALL
    ON SCHEMA {schemaname}
    FROM {username};
REVOKE ALL PRIVILEGES
    ON ALL TABLES
    IN SCHEMA {schemaname}
    FROM {username};
REVOKE ALL PRIVILEGES
    ON ALL FUNCTIONS
    IN SCHEMA {schemaname}
    FROM {username};
REVOKE ALL PRIVILEGES
    ON ALL SEQUENCES
    IN SCHEMA {schemaname}
